          <div className="max-w-xl text-center md:text-left">
            <h2 className="text-4xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight">STRENGTHEN THE NETWORK</h2>
            <p className="text-gray-400 text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed">
              Your feedback helps us optimize the life-saving algorithm. Report issues or suggest improvements directly to the Admin console.
